# Checkbox Group

The `bo-checkbox-group` component allows you to group multiple checkboxes together, providing shared state management, validation, and consistent styling.

## Basic Usage

::: raw
<bo-checkbox-group v-model="selectedOptions">
<bo-checkbox value="option1">Option 1</bo-checkbox>
<bo-checkbox value="option2">Option 2</bo-checkbox>
<bo-checkbox value="option3">Option 3</bo-checkbox>
</bo-checkbox-group>
:::

```vue
<script setup>
	import { ref } from 'vue';
	const selectedOptions = ref(['option1']);
</script>

<bo-checkbox-group v-model="selectedOptions">
  <bo-checkbox value="option1">Option 1</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="option2">Option 2</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="option3">Option 3</bo-checkbox>
</bo-checkbox-group>
```

## With Label and Description

Checkbox groups can include labels and descriptions to provide context.

::: raw
<bo-checkbox-group
v-model="fruits"
label="Select your favorite fruits"
description="Choose one or more options from the list below"

>

    <bo-checkbox value="apple">Apple</bo-checkbox>
    <bo-checkbox value="banana">Banana</bo-checkbox>
    <bo-checkbox value="orange">Orange</bo-checkbox>
    <bo-checkbox value="grape">Grape</bo-checkbox>

</bo-checkbox-group>
:::

```vue
<bo-checkbox-group
	v-model="fruits"
	label="Select your favorite fruits"
	description="Choose one or more options from the list below"
>
  <bo-checkbox value="apple">Apple</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="banana">Banana</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="orange">Orange</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="grape">Grape</bo-checkbox>
</bo-checkbox-group>
```

## Orientation

Checkbox groups can be displayed horizontally or vertically.

::: raw

<div class="space-y-6">
  <div>
    <h4 class="mb-2 font-medium">Vertical (default)</h4>
    <bo-checkbox-group v-model="colors" orientation="vertical">
      <bo-checkbox value="red">Red</bo-checkbox>
      <bo-checkbox value="blue">Blue</bo-checkbox>
      <bo-checkbox value="green">Green</bo-checkbox>
    </bo-checkbox-group>
  </div>
  
  <div>
    <h4 class="mb-2 font-medium">Horizontal</h4>
    <bo-checkbox-group v-model="colors" orientation="horizontal">
      <bo-checkbox value="red">Red</bo-checkbox>
      <bo-checkbox value="blue">Blue</bo-checkbox>
      <bo-checkbox value="green">Green</bo-checkbox>
    </bo-checkbox-group>
  </div>
</div>
:::

```vue
<!-- Vertical (default) -->
<bo-checkbox-group v-model="colors" orientation="vertical">
  <bo-checkbox value="red">Red</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="blue">Blue</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="green">Green</bo-checkbox>
</bo-checkbox-group>

<!-- Horizontal -->
<bo-checkbox-group v-model="colors" orientation="horizontal">
  <bo-checkbox value="red">Red</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="blue">Blue</bo-checkbox>
  <bo-checkbox value="green">Green</bo-checkbox>
</bo-checkbox-group>
```
